Maximus! Maximus!

1281
02:16:18,760 --> 02:16:20,970
Maximus! Maximus!

1282
02:16:21,054 --> 02:16:24,307
Maximus! Maximus! Maximus!

1283
02:16:24,390 --> 02:16:27,393
Maximus! Maximus!

1284
02:16:27,477 --> 02:16:29,771
Maximus! Maximus!

1285
02:16:34,192 --> 02:16:36,361
Maximus.

1286
02:16:36,444 --> 02:16:38,613
Maximus.

1287
02:16:38,696 --> 02:16:40,657
Maximus.

1288
02:16:41,866 --> 02:16:43,951
They call for you.

1289
02:16:45,578 --> 02:16:49,332
The general
who became a slave.

1290
02:16:49,415 --> 02:16:52,669
The slave
who became a gladiator.

1291
02:16:53,920 --> 02:16:57,048
The gladiator
who defied an emperor.

1292
02:16:58,716 --> 02:17:01,344
A striking story.

1293
02:17:01,427 --> 02:17:04,389
Now the people want to know
how the story ends.

1294
02:17:06,891 --> 02:17:09,143
Only a famous death will do.

1295
02:17:10,728 --> 02:17:13,690
And what could be
more glorious...

1296
02:17:13,731 --> 02:17:17,694
than to challenge the Emperor
himself in the great arena?

1297
02:17:20,071 --> 02:17:22,365
You would fight me?

1298
02:17:22,407 --> 02:17:26,119
Why not?
Do you think I'm afraid?

1299
02:17:27,328 --> 02:17:30,123
I think you have been afraid
all your life.

1300
02:17:30,206 --> 02:17:34,335
Unlike Maximus the Invincible,
who knows no fear?

1301
02:17:39,966 --> 02:17:44,262
I knew a man who once said,
" Death smiles at us all.

1302
02:17:44,303 --> 02:17:47,473
All a man can do
is smile back."

1303
02:17:47,557 --> 02:17:50,226
I wonder.

1304
02:17:50,310 --> 02:17:52,729
Did your friend
smile at his own death?

1305
02:17:53,813 --> 02:17:55,732
You must know.

1306
02:17:58,151 --> 02:18:00,486
He was your father.

1307
02:18:03,823 --> 02:18:07,493
You loved my father,
I know.

1308
02:18:07,577 --> 02:18:09,495
But so did l.

1309
02:18:10,580 --> 02:18:12,790
That makes us brothers,
doesn't it?

1310
02:18:15,043 --> 02:18:17,879
Smile for me now, brother.

1311
02:18:21,716 --> 02:18:24,427
- Strap on his armor.

1312
02:18:24,510 --> 02:18:27,221
Conceal the wound.

1313
02:18:32,977 --> 02:18:34,729
Maximus! Maximus!

1314
02:18:34,812 --> 02:18:37,565
Maximus! Maximus!

1315
02:19:19,941 --> 02:19:21,943
Ring formation!

1316
02:19:22,026 --> 02:19:24,821
Ring formation!

1317
02:19:54,350 --> 02:19:57,520
Off with his head, Maximus!

1318
02:21:01,709 --> 02:21:05,380
- Aah!

1319
02:21:12,970 --> 02:21:15,139
Maximus! Maximus! Maximus!

1320
02:21:15,223 --> 02:21:17,600
Quintus, sword!

1321
02:21:17,642 --> 02:21:20,436
Give me your sword!

1322
02:21:22,438 --> 02:21:24,983
Sword! Give me a sword!

1323
02:21:25,066 --> 02:21:27,860
- Sheathe your swords!

1324
02:21:27,944 --> 02:21:30,947
Sheathe yours swords!

1325
02:23:45,540 --> 02:23:47,458
Maximus.

1326
02:23:51,504 --> 02:23:55,008
- Maximus.
- Quintus.

1327
02:23:56,926 --> 02:23:59,846
Free my men.

1328
02:23:59,929 --> 02:24:02,473
Senator Gracchus
is to be reinstated.

1329
02:24:03,558 --> 02:24:05,560
There was a dream
that was Rome.

1330
02:24:06,811 --> 02:24:09,439
It shall be realized.

1331
02:24:09,522 --> 02:24:12,066
These are the wishes
of Marcus Aurelius.

1332
02:24:12,150 --> 02:24:15,069
Free the prisoners!
Go!

1333
02:24:39,010 --> 02:24:40,928
Maximus!

1334
02:24:42,805 --> 02:24:45,099
Lucius is safe.

1335
02:25:00,615 --> 02:25:02,700
Go to them.

1336
02:25:50,873 --> 02:25:53,334
You're home.

1337
02:26:19,402 --> 02:26:22,822
Is Rome worth
one good man's life?

1338
02:26:26,451 --> 02:26:28,703
We believed it once.

1339
02:26:30,788 --> 02:26:32,749
Make us
believe it again.

1340
02:26:37,128 --> 02:26:39,589
He was a soldier of Rome.

1341
02:26:43,009 --> 02:26:45,345
Honor him.

1342
02:26:45,428 --> 02:26:47,847
Who will help me carry him?

1343
02:27:31,808 --> 02:27:34,268
Now we are free.

1344
02:27:39,774 --> 02:27:42,360
I will see you again.

1345
02:27:44,487 --> 02:27:47,073
But not yet.

1346
02:27:47,115 --> 02:27:49,075
Not yet.

